- Customize the deliverable to match EXACTLY what they asked for
- Add specific portfolio piece URL
- Check r/{opp['subreddit']} rules for self-promotion
- Status: PENDING_REVIEW
"""
            safe_path(outfile)
            outfile.write_text(content)
